import React from 'react'
import { Edit, SimpleForm, TextInput, DateInput, PasswordInput, NullableBooleanInput } from 'react-admin'


const UserEdit = (props) => {
  return (
    <Edit title='Edit User' {...props}>
      <SimpleForm>
        <TextInput disabled source='id' />
        <TextInput source='user-name' />
        <TextInput source='email' />
        <NullableBooleanInput label="Sex" source="sex" nullLabel="Other" falseLabel="female" trueLabel/>
        <DateInput source='age' />
        <TextInput disabled source='account-name' />
        <PasswordInput source='password' />
      </SimpleForm>
    </Edit>
  )
}

export default UserEdit
